[normal]on economic progress, including through consideration of the costs, effectiveness and
[normal]perceptions
[normal] of fairness of regulation. They should only adopt a particular approach if
[normal]the benefits justify the costs
[normal]7 
[normal]and it entails the minimum burden compatible with
[normal]achieving their objectives.”, Regulators’ Compliance Code, 2007 
